WEBVTT

00:00.430 --> 00:02.252
My name is Danny McNamara.

00:02.258 --> 00:03.719
When I left the FBI, I thought

00:03.726 --> 00:06.080
my crime-fighting days were
over, but then I learned

00:06.086 --> 00:08.603
that terrorist Karim Farouk
was on the hunt for Cleopatra,

00:08.609 --> 00:10.677
one of the world's
most valuable treasures,

00:10.683 --> 00:12.418
lost for over 2,000 years,

00:12.424 --> 00:14.488
to use her as part of a
massive terror attack.

00:14.494 --> 00:16.450
To find him, I needed some help,

00:16.456 --> 00:18.599
so I went to Lexi Vaziri, a thief.

00:18.605 --> 00:21.240
Excuse me, a master thief.

00:21.246 --> 00:23.499
And my father was killed by Farouk.

00:23.505 --> 00:24.852
I wanted justice.

00:24.858 --> 00:26.103
Lexi wanted revenge.

00:26.109 --> 00:28.444
But neither of us got what we wanted.

00:28.450 --> 00:30.464
Farouk was killed before
we could catch him.

00:30.470 --> 00:33.186
Farouk may be dead,

00:33.192 --> 00:35.405
but his plan for a
massive attack lives on.

00:35.411 --> 00:37.897
And his crew is still out there.

00:40.106 --> 00:42.200
Previously on Blood & Treasure...

00:42.206 --> 00:44.472
This means your mother
was a direct descendant

00:44.478 --> 00:46.444
in the bloodline of Cleopatra.

00:46.450 --> 00:47.617
And so are you.

00:47.623 --> 00:49.951
Your future is our future.

00:49.957 --> 00:51.224
No, thanks.

00:51.553 --> 00:53.287
Just tell us where Cleopatra is.

00:53.293 --> 00:55.053
Ask Everado Sanchez.

00:55.059 --> 00:56.626
He has her, and good riddance.

00:56.632 --> 00:57.732
The narco.

00:59.030 --> 01:00.629
The death of Captain Fabi

01:00.635 --> 01:01.849
is carabinieri business.

01:01.855 --> 01:03.022
We will take care of it.

01:03.028 --> 01:04.569
I broke into Fabi's apartment

01:04.575 --> 01:06.860
and I stole a bunch of
secret files from his office.

01:06.866 --> 01:09.780
Fabi was investigating
something before he died.

01:09.819 --> 01:11.886
A different angle on Farouk.

01:11.954 --> 01:13.254
I think he found something out.

01:13.260 --> 01:14.660
They tracked Farouk's men.

01:14.666 --> 01:16.801
So we have to assume that Farouk's crew

01:16.807 --> 01:18.154
is carrying on with his plan.

01:18.160 --> 01:20.628
And now they've got a biological weapon.

01:27.874 --> 01:30.166
_

01:30.172 --> 01:34.075
This is not goodbye, my love. Hmm?

01:34.413 --> 01:36.748
Papa, I'm scared.

01:36.754 --> 01:37.968
Mira...

01:38.132 --> 01:41.449
everything I do,
everything I've ever done,

01:41.455 --> 01:43.089
is for this family.

01:45.087 --> 01:46.988
Don Everado... the soldiers are coming.

01:46.994 --> 01:48.394
We have to leave now.

01:48.710 --> 01:49.849
Start the plane.

01:49.855 --> 01:50.913
Sí, padrón.

01:54.223 --> 01:56.759
Will you be leaving us forever, papa?

01:56.765 --> 01:58.933
This is only a short trip for business.

01:58.939 --> 02:00.573
I will be back very soon.

02:00.579 --> 02:01.906
Promise?

02:04.029 --> 02:06.062
Sí, mi corazón.

02:12.214 --> 02:15.183
Papa, who is she?

02:15.251 --> 02:17.352
Her name is Cleopatra.

02:17.358 --> 02:20.461
Once she was the greatest
queen in all the world.

02:20.467 --> 02:22.769
As beautiful as you.

02:23.974 --> 02:25.576
I will protect her.

02:25.582 --> 02:28.396
And one day, she will be yours.

02:28.464 --> 02:30.832
Queen Soledad!

02:35.271 --> 02:37.839
I will return soon!

02:37.907 --> 02:39.707
I promise!

