We barely escaped in time.
They're closing in.

03:29.219 --> 03:31.287
We should go underground.

03:31.293 --> 03:33.557
Come out of hiding when the heat is off.

03:33.563 --> 03:35.425
The plan doesn't change.

03:35.431 --> 03:37.865
I followed Farouk. Not you!

03:44.822 --> 03:46.723
Farouk is dead.

03:47.276 --> 03:49.244
But the attack will proceed.

03:49.373 --> 03:51.374
You're being paid by the
same person as before.

03:51.380 --> 03:53.114
Nothing changes.

03:53.182 --> 03:54.315
Get moving.

03:58.985 --> 04:01.025
_

04:01.031 --> 04:03.124
I've never been in a museum off hours

04:03.130 --> 04:05.097
when I wasn't stealing from it.

04:05.103 --> 04:06.594
It's rather peaceful.

04:06.662 --> 04:08.830
Yeah, it's amazing how
much you can enjoy a place

04:08.897 --> 04:10.765
when you're not running
from security guards.

04:10.771 --> 04:12.988
If you do it right, the guards
never know you're there.

04:12.994 --> 04:14.530
But point taken.

04:14.536 --> 04:16.022
Speaking of guards, does Reece

04:16.028 --> 04:17.810
already know about the bio-threat?

04:17.873 --> 04:19.850
No, no, this is standard for protecting

04:19.856 --> 04:21.781
an antiquity as important as Antony.

04:21.786 --> 04:23.112
But we need to warn him about

04:23.118 --> 04:24.702
Farouk's men making a move.

04:25.080 --> 04:27.274
Let them pass, they're with us.

04:27.618 --> 04:29.617
Well, you've had an
interesting few weeks.

04:29.685 --> 04:31.119
Hey, tell me about it, man.

04:31.186 --> 04:32.520
Lexi, this is Rick Yates,

04:32.533 --> 04:33.967
Reece's head of security.

04:33.973 --> 04:36.041
Rick, this is... Lexi Vaziri.

04:36.138 --> 04:37.838
Mr. Reece mentioned me.

04:37.844 --> 04:39.527
More like warned me about...

04:39.595 --> 04:41.963
but he has come around on you, somewhat.

04:41.969 --> 04:43.259
As have I, him.

04:45.095 --> 04:47.363
You know, when you're in a relationship,

04:47.369 --> 04:49.358
friends and family are
part of the package.

04:49.364 --> 04:50.838
Kind of like cousins

04:50.844 --> 04:52.368
who visit each other at holidays.

04:52.374 --> 04:54.003
I don't need to check
my cousins' pockets

04:54.009 --> 04:55.547
when they leave the room.

04:56.023 --> 04:58.646
Well, if it isn't our
heroes of the hour.

04:58.714 --> 05:00.198
Great to have you back, Danny.

05:00.204 --> 05:01.347
Dr. Castillo.

05:01.353 --> 05:02.620
- Danny.
- Hey.

05:02.751 --> 05:06.187
Oh... Jay called me the moment
Antony was recovered.

05:06.193 --> 05:08.017
Actually, more begged than just called.

05:08.023 --> 05:09.390
I had to see him for myself.

05:09.458 --> 05:11.353
The two of you are
going down in history.

05:11.359 --> 05:13.821
- Dr. Castillo.
- Oh, looks like I'm needed.

05:13.827 --> 05:16.331
This is so exciting.

05:16.398 --> 05:19.634
I've convinced Ana to stay,
oversee the restoration.

05:19.640 --> 05:20.897
Arrangements are underway

05:20.903 --> 05:24.205
for a public unveiling
in Cairo next week.

05:26.892 --> 05:29.744
Um... okay, so I've
worked my entire life

05:29.812 --> 05:31.312
for this very moment,

05:31.318 --> 05:34.318
and you two look like I've
just run over your dog.

05:34.324 --> 05:35.557
What's going on?

05:35.563 --> 05:38.486
Jay, we need to move Antony
to a secure location.

05:39.163 --> 05:41.656
See... uh, I'm not sure you've noticed,

05:41.662 --> 05:44.734
but we are surrounded
literally by an army.

05:44.740 --> 05:46.361
Farouk's latest base of operations

05:46.367 --> 05:48.104
had traces of a bio-agent.

05:48.831 --> 05:50.345
He was developing a weapon.

05:50.351 --> 05:52.104
His crew is still out there.

05:52.110 --> 05:53.401
They're not giving up on his plan,

05:53.407 --> 05:54.540
and as far as we know,

05:54.546 --> 05:56.780
that means they want
Antony and Cleopatra.

05:56.972 --> 05:58.873
They're coming for Antony.

06:00.943 --> 06:04.112
Double our security immediately
and call the prime minister.

06:04.118 --> 06:05.842
Make sure that we're
all in communication

06:05.848 --> 06:09.248
about any threats in the
area, I do not care how small.

06:09.845 --> 06:10.978
Okay, kid, don't worry.

06:10.984 --> 06:12.673
We'll put Antony on lockdown.

06:13.040 --> 06:15.189
Meanwhile, any leads on Cleopatra?

06:15.195 --> 06:16.915
Well, the last of the Nazis sold her off

06:16.921 --> 06:18.621
to a drug dealer in the '90s.

06:18.627 --> 06:20.762
I just said that out loud.

06:20.768 --> 06:22.273
Everado Sanchez disappeared,

06:22.279 --> 06:23.993
but I have a friend in the FBI

06:23.999 --> 06:25.651
that can help us track him down.

06:25.657 --> 06:26.925
Then keep me posted.

06:26.931 --> 06:29.499
But... just be careful.

06:29.505 --> 06:31.406
- Yeah.
- Both of you.

06:41.312 --> 06:42.862
How long you gonna keep me here?

06:42.868 --> 06:44.113
I want to go home.

06:44.119 --> 06:46.387
I'm sorry for the delay, Mr. Hardwick.

06:46.455 --> 06:48.156
You'll be on your way
as soon as possible.

06:48.162 --> 06:49.396
And will you be supplying me

06:49.402 --> 06:51.953
with any form of police
protection when you let me go?

06:53.095 --> 06:55.563
I mean, Farouk's men are
still out there, aren't they?

06:55.631 --> 06:57.231
I've got more than a sneaking suspicion

06:57.237 --> 06:59.572
that they're gonna come after
me because I killed him.

06:59.578 --> 07:01.053
No one outside this building knows your

07:01.059 --> 07:02.565
involvement apart from Danny and Lexi.

07:02.571 --> 07:04.027
We're keeping it out of the news.

07:04.033 --> 07:06.502
The Italians have offered
you a hotel room here in Rome

07:06.508 --> 07:08.609
with a police detail
until this is resolved.

07:08.615 --> 07:09.814
How comforting.

07:09.820 --> 07:11.913
I don't suppose I could put in a request

07:11.919 --> 07:13.720
for the Palazzo Naiadi, could I?

07:13.849 --> 07:16.150
We'll see what can be arranged.

07:18.654 --> 07:21.248
Now, I need to talk to you
about another matter...

07:22.658 --> 07:24.740
Related to the Farouk case.

07:25.861 --> 07:29.430
This check was written out

07:29.436 --> 07:30.936
to a Zara Farouk.

07:32.017 --> 07:33.801
Is that a name you ever heard of,

07:33.869 --> 07:35.970
perhaps in your time in captivity?

07:36.038 --> 07:37.638
I don't understand.

07:37.706 --> 07:41.008
I... I thought "Karim Farouk"
was just a nom de guerre

07:41.076 --> 07:43.311
for Rasheed Hegazi.

07:45.865 --> 07:48.066
Look, I want to help you.

07:48.517 --> 07:50.980
I really do, but I'm afraid.

07:52.254 --> 07:55.156
And I'm afraid because
in my year of captivity,

07:55.224 --> 07:57.492
it seemed to me that Karim Farouk

07:57.498 --> 07:59.233
was protected by some very

07:59.239 --> 08:01.440
powerful people in high places.

08:01.563 --> 08:04.198
Anybody that got too close
to the truth about him

08:04.266 --> 08:06.667
or his past were dealt with severely.

08:06.735 --> 08:08.135
Before they were killed.

08:08.203 --> 08:10.505
He may be dead...

08:10.572 --> 08:13.536
But the people protecting
him are still out there.

08:13.816 --> 08:15.340
So...

08:16.845 --> 08:18.563
If I were you...

08:19.948 --> 08:21.349
I'd be very careful

08:21.676 --> 08:23.421
about opening any doors,

08:23.427 --> 08:25.057
because you have no idea

08:25.063 --> 08:27.264
who may be standing on the other side.

08:29.591 --> 08:32.527
I had to pull a few strings
at the FBI to get that.

08:32.594 --> 08:34.861
The United States government
isn't exactly too keen

08:34.868 --> 08:36.424
on discussing Sanchez.

08:36.431 --> 08:37.899
Why is that?

08:37.966 --> 08:39.833
Sanchez was the biggest
narco in the world.

08:39.902 --> 08:42.035
Worth billions with
a rap sheet for days.

08:42.104 --> 08:43.837
DEA spent millions of dollars,

08:43.842 --> 08:45.973
thousands of man-hours finding him.

08:45.979 --> 08:47.603
Just as they had him cornered,

08:47.609 --> 08:49.176
vanished into thin air.

08:49.244 --> 08:51.012
Biggest botch in DEA history.

08:51.079 --> 08:53.347
I think I might have an idea

08:53.642 --> 08:55.510
what might've been there.

08:57.065 --> 08:59.132
Cleopatra's coffin.

08:59.138 --> 09:00.546
Given his appetite for

09:00.552 --> 09:02.141
anything he could make money on,

09:02.147 --> 09:04.014
and his connection to
Steiner, it's not a leap.

09:04.020 --> 09:06.455
Where was the last place
Sanchez was known to be?

09:06.461 --> 09:07.862
He switched off his transponder

09:07.930 --> 09:09.764
when he stopped to refuel in Panama.

09:09.831 --> 09:11.265
Wherever he was headed...

09:11.333 --> 09:13.267
No one's ever seen him
or his plane again.

09:13.724 --> 09:15.692
But I do have this:

09:15.698 --> 09:19.140
DEA wiretaps of Sanchez. All of them.

09:19.207 --> 09:20.975
Including his final call from Panama

09:21.043 --> 09:24.245
to his lieutenant
Miguel Navarro in 1993.

09:24.251 --> 09:25.688
How's your Spanish?

09:25.694 --> 09:27.949
Better than her Serbian,
worse than her Italian.

